title: LUCIFER Season 5 Ending Explained! Part 2 and Season 6 Theories
author: Think Story

description:
In this video we take a deep dive, review, recap and explain the ending to Netflix's LUCIFER Season 5 as well as offer theories and predictions for Part 2 and Season 6.
